title: Highlanders Win Three In A Row; Defeat Summit 2-0 (Cairn University Highlanders Athletics)
text: ( Source : Cairn University Highlanders Athletics ) Langhorne, PA - Cairn men's soccer won their third CSAC shutout in a row on Monday afternoon, after their 2-0 defeat of Summit University. Noah Egelkamp ( Havertown, PA ) and Brady Dorman
